OL,3,CBus workers agree pay deal to end
OL,4,Cthreat of strike action
OL,6,FWorkers for Arriva North East have
OL,7,Fagreed an increased pay deal ending
OL,8,Fthe threat of strike action.
OL,10,FMore than 300 drivers and engineers
OL,11,Fhad voted for industrial action - with
OL,12,Fstrikes planned for two weeks this
OL,13,Fmonth.
OL,15,FIt has now been agreed meaning all
OL,16,Fstaff at the Ashington and Blyth
OL,17,Fdepots will receive a 6.1% pay
OL,18,Fincrease which Unite the Union say
OL,19,Fmatches the best bus company pay in
OL,20,Fthe region.
