OL,3,CBus workers agree pay deal to end
OL,4,Cthreat of strike action
OL,6,FWorkers will also receive a #350 lump
OL,7,Fsum payment.
OL,9,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,10,Fsaid: "Unite members at Arriva
OL,11,FNorthumbria should be congratulated on
OL,12,Ftheir hard-fought campaign that has
OL,13,Fseen them receive a significant and
OL,14,Fwell-deserved pay increase.
OL,16,F"This shows the strength of the union
OL,17,Fmovement and why Unite will always
OL,18,Fback its members in their disputes
OL,19,Fwith employers who think they can get
OL,20,Faway with underpaying their staff."
